title: Wooden Mosque
text: The Wooden Mosque () is a unique <a href="mosque">mosque</a> situated near the south-east of the city of <a href="Nishapur">Nishapur</a>. This mosque has been built completely by <a href="wood">wood</a>. This <a href="mosque">mosque</a> is one of the <a href="Tourist%20attraction">tourist attractions</a> of the <a href="Nishapur%20County">county of Nishapur</a> and is situated inside a <a href="garden">garden</a>. There are also some <a href="Handicraft">handicraft shops</a>, a <a href="restaurant">restaurant</a>, and other wooden buildings inside the garden of the Wooden Mosque.
